{"arkId":"cl010095289","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010095289","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"La Jonction des deux mers (la M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e et l\u0027Atlantique)","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"La Jonction des deux mers (la M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e et l\u0027Atlantique)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1686","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [SCULPT] Salle 105 - Cour Puget, Salle 105 - Partie basse","room":"Salle 105, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau -1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1686,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Regnaud, Jean","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1697","place":"Brest","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Le N\u00e8gre, Pierre","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Fondeur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q52292329"},{"label":"France \u00cele-de-France Paris","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 4233","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"ENT 1989.02","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"m\u00e9daillon","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,045","displayDimension":"0,045 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"0,765","displayDimension":"0,765 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"bronze \u00e0 patine brune","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"place des victoires (France-\u003EParis-\u003Eplace)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Deux s\u00e9ries de m\u00e9daillons en bronze. Proviennent du d\u00e9cor des quatre pyl\u00f4nes \u00e9lev\u00e9s aux angles de la place des Victoires \u00e0 Paris, ouverte et b\u00e2tie \u00e0 la gloire du roi Louis XIV et de la paix de Nim\u00e8gue (1679) par Fran\u00e7ois d\u0027Aubusson (1632-1691), duc de La Feuillade, mar\u00e9chal de France. Pyl\u00f4nes d\u00e9molis en 1718. \r\nDeuxi\u00e8me s\u00e9rie de m\u00e9daillons d\u00e9corant le pyl\u00f4ne \u00e0 l\u0027encoignure de la rue d\u0027Aubusson (actuellement rue Croix-des-Petits-Champs).\r\nM\u00e9daillons appartenant \u00e0 une s\u00e9rie de six m\u00e9daillons command\u00e9s le 12 ao\u00fbt 1686 par contrat pass\u00e9 entre le duc de La Feuillade, Jean Arnould (qui signe Regnault) et Pierre Le N\u00e8gre. Inventori\u00e9s le 5 septembre 1687 sur la place des Victoires par le corps de la Ville. Vente de la collection Lapeyri\u00e8re, 19 Avril 1825, n\u00b0 25. Acquis par George III (1738-1820), roi d\u0027Angleterre. Don de dernier vers 1830 \u00e0 Lady Conyngham, \u00e9pouse du marquis de Conyngham \u00e0 Slane Castle (Irlande) jusqu\u0027en 1980.\r\nM\u00e9daillon de la Jonction : vente anonyme, Monaco, 27 mai 1980, n\u00b0 1150. Collection particuli\u00e8re, \u00c9tats-Unis d\u0027Am\u00e9rique. Vente anonyme, New York, 22 novembre 1988, n\u00b0 226. Commerce d\u0027art, Paris ; acquis en 1989 (comit\u00e9 du 9 f\u00e9vrier, conseil du 20 f\u00e9vrier, arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 20 f\u00e9vrier 1989).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"09\/02\/1989","startYear":1989,"endYear":1989},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"20\/02\/1989","startYear":1989,"endYear":1989}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"material":[{"value":"bronze"}],"technic":[{"value":"\u00e0 patine brune"}],"place":[{"value":"place des victoires"}],"objectType":[{"value":"m\u00e9daillon"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Le Roi est mort !, Le Roi est mort - Louis XIV - 1715, cat. exp. (Versailles (France), Ch\u00e2teau - Domaine national de Versailles, 2015), Paris, Tallandier, Ch\u00e2teau de Versailles, 2015","bibliographyDate":"2015","bibliographyDetail":"p. 154, ill. 155, n\u00b0 37","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Gaborit, Jean-Ren\u00e9 (dir.), Sculpture fran\u00e7aise II - Renaissance et Temps Modernes, vol. 1 et 2, Paris, \u00c9ditions de la R\u00e9union des mus\u00e9es nationaux, 1998","bibliographyDate":"1998","bibliographyDetail":"p. 561-562","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Nouvelles acquisitions du D\u00e9partement des Sculptures (1988-1991), Paris, 1992","bibliographyDate":"1992","bibliographyDetail":"p. 58-61, n\u00b0 18","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Souchal, Fran\u00e7ois ; La Moureyre-Gavoty, Fran\u00e7oise\u00a0(de) ; Dumuis, Henriette, French sculptors of the 17th and 18th centuries  : the reign of Louis XIV, 3, Oxford \/ Londres, Cassirer ; Faber, 1977-1987","bibliographyDate":"1981","bibliographyDetail":"t. I, 1977, p. 257","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[{"value":"Le Roi est mort, Versailles (France), Ch\u00e2teau - Domaine national de Versailles, 26\/10\/2015 - 21\/02\/2016 "}],"relatedWork":[{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010093924","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/col